```{r}
data <- read.csv("var_19.csv")
tail(data)
str(data)
```

```{r}
data$Treatment <- as.factor(data$Treatment)

```

```{r}
model <- lm(Output ~ Treatment, data = data)
summary(model)
```
```{r}
anova(model)
```
```{r}
(anovag_Sum_Sq_2 <- anova(model)$"Sum Sq"[2])
```
```{r}
(anovag_Sum_Sq_1 <- anova(model)$"Sum Sq"[1])
```


```{r}
gi <- lm(Output ~ Treatment - 1, data = data)
anova(gi)
```
```{r}
(anovamgi_Sum_Sq_1 <- anova(gi)$"Sum Sq"[1])
```

```{r}
(anovamgi_Sum_Sq_1 <- anova(gi)$"Sum Sq"[2])
```
